                        <hr>⚠️ <strong>Weather Notice</strong> ⚠️
                        <div style="text-align: left; font-size: 12px;">This
                          information is compiled by Apex Wx based on available
                          computer models and data and may not reflect current
                          conditions or later forecast updates. Always visit <span
                            style="font-size: 12px;"><a href="https://www.weather.gov/car/"
                              title="NWS Caribou, Maine">NWS Caribou</a></span>
                          for the latest official watches, warnings, and
                          advisories for northern Maine, especially during
                          severe/extreme weather events.</div>
                        <div style="text-align: left; font-size: 12px;"><br>
                        </div>
                        <div style="text-align: left; font-size: 12px;">No
                          guarantees or warranties, expressed or implied, are
                          provided due to inaccuracies, errors, and/or defects
                          in data feeds, instruments, and computer weather
                          models that are beyond the forecaster's control.The
                          accuracy, relevance, timeliness, or completeness of
